title: Tori Spelling keeps casual while joined by Brody Jenner and Josie Canseco at Halloween kick-off
text:
Tori Spelling and one of her five kids were among the celebrity guests at the friends and family preview of Nights of the Jack in Calabasas, California.

The 46 year old BH90210 star-creator took in the event with her youngest son Beau, while Brody Jenner also arrived with new girlfriend Josie Canseco.

The friends and family preview night took place before the attraction opens to the general public, which runs from October 3 to November 3.

Tori and Beau: Tori Spelling and one of her five kids were among the celebrity guests at the friends and family preview of Nights of the Jack in Calabasas, California

Brody and Josie: Brody Jenner, 36, also sported a slightly matching black outfit with his new girlfriend, Josie Canseco, 22

Spelling was wearing a lime green and grey striped sweater plus a gold braided necklace for her outing with young Beau.

She also wore dark blue jeans and black shoes while she hit the red carpet with her son Beau.

Beau was wearing a white dress shirt under a grey cardigan with a monster face on it, plus brown pants and black shoes.

Tori's look: Spelling was wearing a lime green and grey striped sweater plus a gold braided necklace for her outing with young Beau

Tori is coming off the hit Fox reboot BH90210, a reboot of the original 1990s hit Beverly Hills 90210, with the original cast returning.

She also appeared as the Unicorn on Fox's The Masked Singer during the first season.

Brody Jenner, 36, also sported a slightly matching black outfit with his new girlfriend, Josie Canseco, 22.

New couple: Jenner was wearing a black Mad Hueys sweatshirt with matching black pants and black Adidas shoes

Jenner was wearing a black Mad Hueys sweatshirt with matching black pants and black Adidas shoes.

Canseco was wearing a black Dogtown sweatshirt with grey spandex shorts and white Nike sneakers.

She was seen giving Jenner a kiss on the cheek as they hung out on the red carpet.

Sweet: The couple looked very in love

Smooch: The model gave the reality star a kiss

New couple: Jenner and Canseco were first spotted together in West Hollywood in August, shortly after Jenner split from his girlfriend Kaitlynn Carter, who has been dating Miley Cyrus

Jenner and Canseco were first spotted together in West Hollywood in August, shortly after Jenner split from his girlfriend Kaitlynn Carter, who has been dating Miley Cyrus.

The 22 year old Josie is the daughter of former Major League Baseball star Jose Canseco and his ex-wife, model Jessica Canseco.

Josie was Playboy's Playmate of the Month in June 2016, and she made her runway debut at the 2018 Victoria's Secret Fashion Show.
